### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### WhatsApp Sticker Module — Test Requests
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Replace {{variables}} with actual values before running.

### ─── 1. Upload sticker (Super Admin) ──────────
POST http://localhost:4000/whatsapp/stickers/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Happy Cat
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

funny
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

cat
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="happy_cat.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-sticker.png
------boundary--

### ─── 2. List all stickers (Any Admin) ─────────
GET http://localhost:4000/whatsapp/stickers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── 3. Send sticker to WhatsApp (Tenant Admin) ───
POST http://localhost:4000/whatsapp/stickers/send
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "919876543210",
  "stickerId": "{{stickerId}}",
  "consent": true
}

### ─── 4. Delete sticker (Super Admin) ──────────
DELETE http://localhost:4000/whatsapp/stickers/{{stickerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
